channel.title: Model command XD
channel.description:
hi i've trying to make some models. but i've seen a tutorial how to add them but that wont work... thats the command addmodels, addmodel ####<----id or ::addmodel ####<-----still id xD
so how can i add this command? or how is that look like?

item.title: Model command XD
item.dc:creator: @Telenim Telenim
item.description:
@Telenim wrote:

[quote=“sjoukjeowns, post:4, topic:326431”]Search at client.java ctrl+f then search “model” perhaps u can find yours![/quote][quote=“Telenim, post:3, topic:326431”]The command isn’t in the server. It is a client command, also try ::add model ####

(With the space…)[/quote]

The command should already be in the client, it’s in 90% of clients that you can download. Try the command with a space after add and before model.
